,{"pid":"29c0af92bb54000df86cf1715c51baf25a3581e4","tid":446400,"uid":100347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T16:24:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cda415356156f6faf448013917b4c31802e7508f","tid":446400,"uid":144409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T14:17:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔係話要插你定點<br />\n不過你一路要讀者拋開三國無雙固有印象<br />\n但係又用返張星彩呢個暗榮自創名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n張星彩係野史到一直都有出現"},{"pid":"7dcdc4338d1ab27baabff855caa84a8db0d9e65f","tid":446400,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T14:04:11.000Z","msg":"劉備的遺命，他臨死前的幻覺，甚至孔明贈給後主的「大漢美女圖鑑」⋯⋯全都指向一名關鍵的人物 － 傳說中會施妖法，能穿越時空，使英靈起死回生的神秘女子。到底此女子是誰？立即點擊觀看：<br />\n<br />\n第七回 臨終遺言： <a href=\"https://oice.com/story/3b700d86f19c4fa3af75c9947bef6d0f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2F3b700d86f19c4fa3af75c9947bef6d0f&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=3d4dece6\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/3b700d86f19c4fa3af75c9947bef6d0f</a><br />\n<br />\n第八回 後主娶妃： <a href=\"https://oice.com/story/9067a484b5904bda8dce047f2c20a245 \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2F9067a484b5904bda8dce047f2c20a245%20&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=b0a12fd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/9067a484b5904bda8dce047f2c20a245 </a>"},{"pid":"bb143cefdeee50a82c0200c2d2cfe267425e2c9c","tid":446400,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-20T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"《我的關銀屏哪有這麼易死》今天更新了本季的最後兩回了。在跟南蠻王戰鬥的過程中，趙廣終於了解到所謂起死回生的「妖術」是什麼回事：咦，咒語竟是「波耶波羅密」？！ <br />\n<br />\n各位如果喜歡這個故事，請下載 oice app（ <a href=\"https://oice.app.link/download\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.app.link%2Fdownload&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=11229242\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.app.link/download</a> )，給這故事一個 like，若能付費訂閱 oice app，更是感激。 <br />\n<br />\n讀者的支持是作者繼續創作的資源和動力！ <br />\n<br />\n第九回－入侵南蠻： <a href=\"https://oice.com/story/7fc3a71845934b239b4911a837950536\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2F7fc3a71845934b239b4911a837950536&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=83299e30\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/7fc3a71845934b239b4911a837950536</a> <br />\n第十回－擒賊擒王： <a href=\"https://oice.com/story/d3cff768adbb45d2ad28b17f15088d63\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2Fd3cff768adbb45d2ad28b17f15088d63&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=f7b4b0f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/d3cff768adbb45d2ad28b17f15088d63</a>"},{"pid":"e35367022c6980b2bea82f01882a711e00e3b711","tid":446400,"uid":91990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-29T13:11:15.000Z","msg":"原作者凌晨說要儲夠人氣才寫下去⋯⋯我作為忠實粉絲當然無法忍受這漫長的等待。於是，我接力亂寫下去了。大家，不用 Like 我的故事，未看完《我的關銀屏哪有這麼易死》第一季的，快搶入去看看，記得 Like！<br />\n什麼？？孔明原來懂得「覇氣」？？！！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://oice.com/story/e5c3360cae18435584603f9799ab8d99?lang=zh-HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Foice.com%2Fstory%2Fe5c3360cae18435584603f9799ab8d99%3Flang%3Dzh-HK&d=1NZAhb25l1WoeQK%2FM0wu7UkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=aa715631\" target=\"_blank\">https://oice.com/story/e5c3360cae18435584603f9799ab8d99?lang=zh-HK</a>"}]}